&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a typical sales role. This is a call to professionals who sell with elegance, advise with authority, and understand that, for discerning travelers, the journey is everything. Kensington&#39;s Cruise Experts are the architects of extraordinary adventures - designing bespoke Land &amp;amp; Sea itineraries that take clients to the far edges of the earth, from the polar ice fields to the Galapagos, from hidden Mediterranean coves to the untouched rivers of Asia. You will not just book travel, you transform it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From the moment of first contact to welcoming your travelers home, you will guide high-end clientele through a unique and exhilarating portfolio of luxury products and experiences. You will offer an array of premium-to-luxury cruise line products, along with meticulously curated pre- and post-cruise experiences, including private guides, charter flights, luxury lodges, and immersive cultural experiences.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Cruise Expert, you will own the full sales cycle with confidence: uncovering each client&#39;s vision in the discovery call, navigating vessel selection and cabin categories, coordinating logistics, and closing with conviction. You will action incoming leads and cultivate a book of loyal, high-net-worth clients who return to you again and again because no one else delivers at your level.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section id=&quot;st-additionalInformation&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead high-touch discovery conversations that reveal what moves your clients - then design journeys that exceed those expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft seamless Land &amp;amp; Sea itineraries that combine bespoke fly-cruise options, luxury lodges, private guides, and multi-country extensions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage availability, quotes, and bookings with precision, working with our curated network of world-class cruise partners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and deepen a portfolio of loyal, high-net-worth clients through exceptional service, proactive communication, and a consultative sales approach that prioritizes the client experience first.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring destinations to life through vivid storytelling and passion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently meet and exceed monthly revenue targets while elevating the client experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt

