&lt;li&gt;Maintaining organized records of partner communications, campaign documentation, and reporting materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with internal marketing, sales, and product teams to support partnership initiatives as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
